getAllContextVOForBaseVO

public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getAllContextVOForBaseVO(java.lang.String flexfieldCode,
                                                                                            java.lang.Long applicationId,
                                                                                            java.lang.String flexUsageCode,
                                                                                            java.lang.String groupName,
                                                                                            oracle.jbo.server.DBTransaction tx)
This api is returns a map of context VO name and context details for a given flexfield. The list is calculated from the metadata in the database. The details returned might be different from the generated artifacts in MDS in case there are some undeployed metadata changes in the database. The API would return only the non-interface VO's names for the contexts.

Parameters:
flexFieldCode - : Flexfield code for which the context vo map is needed
applicationId - : Application id
flexUsageCode - : Only vo names for contexts enabled for the passed in usage code are returned.
groupName - : Only context VO names for thepassed in group are returned.
tx - : transaction object.
Returns:
- Hashmap with Key : Context Code Value : Vo Name
